iro Matsumoto (53-17-4, 18 KO) defends his RISE bantamweight title against top challenger Masahi Kumura (24-7, 12 KO) and Australian KO artists Chadd Collins (64-18-2, 32) defends his RISE super lightweight championship against the great Kento Haraguchi (25-4-1, 14 KO)." type="episode" contentRating="PG-13" duration="13398000" grandparentArt="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentRatingKey="6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentThumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg" grandparentTitle="GLORY Kickboxing" grandparentType="show" index="7" originallyAvailableAt="2025-02-08T00:00:00Z" parentIndex="0" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://partner-upload-assets.wurl.com/glory_kickboxing/FAST_Graphics_G102.jpg" title="GLORY 102 Featherweight Grand Prix" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="GLORY 102 Featherweight Grand Prix" type="coverArt" url="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg"/><Image alt="GLORY 102 Featherweight Grand Prix" type="coverPoster" url="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg"/><Image alt="GLORY 102 Featherweight Grand Prix" type="snapshot" url="https://partner-upload-assets.wurl.com/glory_kickboxing/FAST_Graphics_G102.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="sports" tag="Sports" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1777523058" duration="13398000" endsAt="1777536456" id="69f15143e49645c729b8dacc" onAir="0" pr